### Test Storage Endpoints
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Storage Limits (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/storage/limits
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Generate Upload URL for Photo
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/upload-url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportId": "9b020ecb-0009-4e81-bfcb-1ad3eb666b5c",
  "mediaType": "photo",
  "mimeType": "image/jpeg",
  "fileSizeBytes": 2048000,
  "fileName": "jalan-rusak.jpg"
}

### 3. Generate Upload URL for Video
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/upload-url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportId": "9b020ecb-0009-4e81-bfcb-1ad3eb666b5c",
  "mediaType": "video",
  "mimeType": "video/mp4",
  "fileSizeBytes": 15728640,
  "fileName": "video-laporan.mp4"
}

### 4. Generate Upload URL for Progress Photo (Officer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/upload-url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportId": "9b020ecb-0009-4e81-bfcb-1ad3eb666b5c",
  "mediaType": "progress_photo",
  "mimeType": "image/png",
  "fileSizeBytes": 3145728,
  "fileName": "progress-1.png"
}

### 5. Generate Batch Upload URLs (Multiple Photos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/batch-upload-url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportId": "9b020ecb-0009-4e81-bfcb-1ad3eb666b5c",
  "files": [
    {
      "mediaType": "photo",
      "mimeType": "image/jpeg",
      "fileSizeBytes": 2048000,
      "fileName": "photo-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "mediaType": "photo",
      "mimeType": "image/png",
      "fileSizeBytes": 1536000,
      "fileName": "photo-2.png"
    },
    {
      "mediaType": "photo",
      "mimeType": "image/webp",
      "fileSizeBytes": 1024000,
      "fileName": "photo-3.webp"
    }
  ]
}

### 6. Test File Too Large (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/upload-url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportId": "9b020ecb-0009-4e81-bfcb-1ad3eb666b5c",
  "mediaType": "photo",
  "mimeType": "image/jpeg",
  "fileSizeBytes": 15728640,
  "fileName": "too-large.jpg"
}

### 7. Test Invalid MIME Type (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/storage/upload-url
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportId": "9b020ecb-0009-4e81-bfcb-1ad3eb666b5c",
  "mediaType": "photo",
  "mimeType": "image/gif",
  "fileSizeBytes": 2048000,
  "fileName": "animated.gif"
}

